<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>TWZ</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 28 Jun 2026 13:45:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>自和平备忘录签署以来，美国对伊朗进行首次打击（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-carries-out-first-strike-on-iran-since-peace-memorandum-signed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这次袭击是对伊朗昨天袭击一艘离开霍尔木兹海峡的货船的回应。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-carries-out-first-strike-on-iran-since-peace-memorandum-signed"&gt;自签署和平备忘录（更新）以来美国对伊朗进行首次打击的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jun 2026 00:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-carries-out-first-strike-on-iran-since-peace-memorandum-signed</guid></item><item><title>地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-197</link><description>&lt;p&gt;还记得……天空吗？&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;帖子&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-197"&gt;《地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情》&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 20:54:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-197</guid></item><item><title>C-17 货机飞往加勒比海参与委内瑞拉地震救援工作</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/c-17-globemaster-iii-jets-flowing-to-caribbean-for-venezuela-earthquake-relief-effort</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这些航班是美国向委内瑞拉提供人道主义援助的军事努力的一部分。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/c-17-globemaster-iii-jets-flowing-to-caribbean-for-venezuela-earthquake-relief-effort"&gt;C-17 货机飞往加勒比海参加委内瑞拉地震救援工作&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 19:14:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/c-17-globemaster-iii-jets-flowing-to-caribbean-for-venezuela-earthquake-relief-effort</guid></item><item><title>官方消息：F-35 交付时不带雷达</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/its-official-f-35s-are-now-being-delivered-without-radars</link><description>&lt;p&gt;新型 AN/APG-85 雷达交付的延迟与继续困扰 F-35 项目的其他问题密切相关。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/its-official-f-35s-are-now-being-delivered-without-radars"&gt;官方帖子：F-35 现在交付时不带雷达，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 18:41:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/its-official-f-35s-are-now-being-delivered-without-radars</guid></item><item><title>加拿大抛出曲线球，表示有兴趣加入 GCAP 第六代战斗机计划</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/canada-throws-a-curveball-as-it-signals-interest-in-joining-gcap-sixth-gen-fighter-program</link><description>&lt;p&gt;此举出台之际，渥太华正在考虑拆分其战斗机机队，同时扩大美国以外的防务伙伴关系，但时机是一个问题。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/canada-throws-a-curveball-as-it-signals-interest-in-joining-gcap-sixth-gen-fighter-program"&gt;加拿大抛出一个曲线球，表示有兴趣加入 GCAP 第六代战斗机计划，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 16:27:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/canada-throws-a-curveball-as-it-signals-interest-in-joining-gcap-sixth-gen-fighter-program</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击货船后暂停通过霍尔木兹海峡的船只计划</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/plan-to-move-ships-through-strait-of-hormuz-paused-after-iran-strikes-cargo-vessel</link><description>&lt;p&gt;霍尔木兹海峡最近发生的一系列行动是在航运再次开始流经该海峡时发生的。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/plan-to-move-ships-through-strait-of-hormuz-paused-after-iran-strikes-cargo-vessel"&gt;伊朗袭击货船后暂停通过霍尔木兹海峡的船舶运输计划&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 00:10:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/plan-to-move-ships-through-strait-of-hormuz-paused-after-iran-strikes-cargo-vessel</guid></item><item><title>具有讽刺意味的是，白宫想要突袭海军 E-2 账户来支付美国空军 E-7 的费用</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/in-an-ironic-turn-of-events-white-house-wants-to-raid-navy-e-2-account-to-pay-for-usaf-e-7s</link><description>&lt;p&gt;五角大楼曾试图取消 E-7 并增加 E-2 机队，然后史诗狂怒行动发生了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/in-an-ironic-turn-of-events-white-house-wants-to-raid-navy-e-2-account-to-pay-for-usaf-e-7s"&gt;具有讽刺意味的是，白宫想要突袭海军 E-2 帐户来支付美国空军 E-7 的费用，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 23:22:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/in-an-ironic-turn-of-events-white-house-wants-to-raid-navy-e-2-account-to-pay-for-usaf-e-7s</guid></item><item><title>视频疯传，波音 777 飞行员驾驶波音喷气式飞机进行极低飞行</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/boeing-777-pilots-take-on-extremely-low-pass-by-boeing-jet-captured-in-viral-video</link><description>&lt;p&gt;当飞机在跑道上空以非常低的高度倾斜时，其巨大机翼的尖端距地面仅几英尺。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/boeing-777-pilots-take-on-extremely-low-pass-by-boeing-jet-captured-in-viral-video"&gt;病毒视频中捕捉到的波音 777 飞行员驾驶波音喷气式飞机进行极低飞行的视频&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 20:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/boeing-777-pilots-take-on-extremely-low-pass-by-boeing-jet-captured-in-viral-video</guid></item><item><title>美国空军希望拥有射程高达 1,000 英里的空对空导弹</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-wants-air-to-air-missile-with-a-whopping-1000-mile-range</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国空军希望通过真正的“杀伤网”武器来超越其最新、最强大的空对空导弹能力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-wants-air-to-air-missile-with-a-whopping-1000-mile-range"&gt;美国空军想要射程高达 1,000 英里的空对空导弹&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 18:32:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-wants-air-to-air-missile-with-a-whopping-1000-mile-range</guid></item><item><title>特朗普将批准为土耳其卡恩战斗机出售重要的 F110 涡轮风扇发动机</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/trump-set-to-clear-critical-f110-turbofan-engine-sale-for-turkeys-kaan-fighter</link><description>&lt;p&gt;期待已久的转让将使土耳其的卡恩战斗机保持在正轨，同时引发人们对 F-35 是否重返谈判桌的猜测。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/trump-set-to-clear-critical-f110-turbofan-engine-sale-for-turkeys-kaan-fighter"&gt;特朗普准备批准土耳其卡恩战斗机关键 F110 涡轮风扇发动机销售的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 16:17:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/trump-set-to-clear-critical-f110-turbofan-engine-sale-for-turkeys-kaan-fighter</guid></item></channel></rss>